      "id": "stock_sentinel_basic",
      "title": "股票哨兵基础问答",
      "type": "assistant_turn",
      "skillId": "stock_sentinel",
      "domainId": "finance",
      "question": "帮我看一下比亚迪今天有哪些重大消息，会不会影响我关注的股票？",
