        "finalAnswer": "股票哨兵已生成信息摘要：模拟消息显示关注公司出现重大信息变化；本提醒仅作信息摘要，非投资建议。",
        "toolName": "web_search",
        "toolSummary": "alpha mock 已返回股票哨兵消息面摘要。"
      },
      "remoteExpectations": {
        "answerFragments": ["比亚迪", "重大消息", "投资建议"],
        "eventTypes": [
          "turn_started",
          "plan_updated",
          "search_query_generated",
          "tool_use_requested",
          "tool_result_received",
          "observation_assessed",
          "assistant.model.interaction",
          "final_answer"
        ]
